INSTALL
-------
sendxmpp requires perl 5.x, Getopt::Long and Net::XMPP.

$ tar xvfz sendxmpp-(version).tar.gz
$ cd sendxmpp-(version)
$ perl Makefile.PL
$ make
$ make install

This will install under /usr/local; to install under another prefix, for exampl;e "/usr", do:

$ perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=/usr

instead.

